    CertManager["cert-manager /<br/>deploying operator"] -.->|"provisions TLS certs<br/>(hot-reloaded)"| KRP

    %% Optional External
    KRP -.->|"OIDC discovery + JWKS<br/>HTTPS/443<br/>(when configured)"| OIDCIssuer["OIDC Identity Provider"]

